cmusic
======
CMusic 2.0, play online music!



=========
DOWNLOAD
=========
$ git clone https://github.com/remrain/cmusic.git



=============
INSTALLATION
=============
First, set your player

$ cd cmusic
$ vi conf/cmusic.json

If you do not have mplayer, set you player by modify 'player.cmd', example:
player : {
    "cmd" : ["player", "-mp3", "-url"]
}

And you can set mp3 rate by modify 'baidu_music.rate', example:
baidu_music : {
    rate : 320
}


Then add cmusic/bin to PATH

$ PATH=$PATH:/your/path/to/cmusic/bin
$ echo "PATH=$PATH:/your/path/to/cmusic/bin" >> ~/.bash_profile



============
LET'S PLAY
============
$ cmusic list                      # list all channels
$ cmusic play 2                    # play channel 2
$ cmusic like                      # i like current song, cmusic will mark it
$ cmusic show                      # show name, artist, etc of current song
$ cmusic play                      # play next song
$ cmusic bore                      # current song is boring, do not play it any more
$ cmusic stop                      # stop player
$ ls $HOME/.cmusic                 # cmusic write temp file here



